  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Senior Cook/ Cook",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Requirements</strong></u></p><p>The Snr./Cook will be required to assist with the following basic food preparation tasks and be capable of instructing subordinates to:</p><ul><li>Food preparation and cooking for residents and employees</li><li>Preparation of foods which are to be served as part of special or therapeutic diets for residents</li><li>Ensure food are stored in the correct temperatures</li><li>Ensure food are correctly labelled and expiry dates are strictly adhered</li><li>Oversee the preparation and distribution of meal distribution</li><li>Assist with menu planning</li><li>Minimizes food waste through proper control of portioning and storage of food items</li><li>Maintain overall cleanliness of kitchen</li><li>Ensure members of the Kitchen team are following food safety procedures in the kitchen</li><li>Clean and perform basic maintenance of stoves, work area etc. Dispose garbage from the food service area</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Qualification and Experiences</strong></p><ul><li>O' Level or equivalent qualification</li><li>Basic Food Hygiene certificate (WSQ Food & Beverage Safety & Hygiene Policies and Procedures)</li><li>At least 2 years of relevant work experience.</li></ul>",
